@node HONOR "Honorable Passage"

@{b}Honorable Passage@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = VI(U)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 1W
Artist  = Jeff Miracola

Text(VI): Prevent all damage to you or target creature from any one source.
          If that source is red, Honorable Passage deals to the source's
          controller an amount of damage equal to the amount of damage
          prevented.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_H.guide/HONOR}

